race.description: Prestige Jayco Emerging Stars Ht 10 Maiden Plate
race.comment: GOLDEN SPRITZ (2) is knocking on the door having placed in all three runs to date, firmly in the market each time. He hit the line strongly after drawing the inside gate here over 1107m last time out, giving the indication this trip would now be suitable. From the draw, he lands in a great spot and that can prove the difference. TEN WARRIORS (4) resumes and is interesting. He placed in every run last campaign, beaten 6 lengths by the Group class Bacash first up, ending up over 1600m when close up behind subsequent G1 placegetter Zambardo. This looks a nice race for him, he rates well. STORM LEOPARD (11) is a gelding by Ghaiyyath on debut for the Hayes yard who should be ready to run well. THINKIMACELEBRITY (12) ran a solid race on debut and should take beating from the inside gate.
